      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "RISE AND RESIST (4) did little and finished ninth over 1400m at Sunshine Coast Poly last start, a less impressive effort than his first-up sixth at Sunshine Coast the run before. Won't find this as tough so he is perfectly placed to score. CIRCUS MAXIMUS (2) showed good early speed from the inside draw last start before finishing third over 1000m at Barcaldine. Has the class to take care of this field. LOCK IN (3) returns from a spell of six months and is having his first run for a new yard. Finished sixth at Sunshine Coast over 1400m when first-up last time in work. Can make his presence felt. BOOM FLYER (5) ran below expectations last start, finishing ninth at Tambo over 1000m. Looks well placed so expect a better run this time.",
